Deep beneath its glistening hot sands, large pools of water form when the rare rains arrive during the monsoon season. As the water seeps down, it combines with the mineral rich desert salt to form a thick saline mixture.This is pumped up and left to dry in the salt pans, creating dunes of one of the purest forms of salts found anywhere. Monsoon rains replenish the water levels each season creating a sustainable cycle.The hand-harvested salt crystals are then cleaned and packed, readied for delivery to customers across the world. Lunn Desert Salt are harvested twice each year. The salt harvested during summer is dried under a very hot sun quickly creating sun-tanned crystals.The winter harvest salt, dried over a longer period of time creating sparkling white crystals. Desert Salt is ideal for daily cooking as it not only lends extra flavour to the dishes, but it is also rich in minerals that are important in maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Lunn Salt is Fair Trade Certified salt. Hand-Harvested in sustainable way, Lunn Desert Salt is completely free of micro-plastics found in sea salt."

Deep beneath its glistening hot sands, large pools of water form when the rare rains arrive during the monsoon season. As the water seeps down, it combines with the mineral rich desert salt to form a thick saline mixture.This is pumped up and left to dry in the salt pans, creating dunes of one of the purest forms of salts found anywhere. Monsoon rains replenish the water levels each season creating a sustainable cycle.The hand-harvested salt crystals are then cleaned and packed, readied for delivery to customers across the world. Lunn Desert Salt are harvested twice each year. The salt harvested during summer is dried under a very hot sun quickly creating sun-tanned crystals.The winter harvest salt, dried over a longer period of time creating sparkling white crystals. Desert Salt is ideal for daily cooking as it not only lends extra flavour to the dishes, but it is also rich in minerals that are important in maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Lunn Salt is Fair Trade Certified salt. Hand-Harvested in sustainable way, Lunn Desert Salt is completely free of micro-plastics found in sea salt."
